            "time": null,
            "author_sender": "Joseph Zangrilli (JZ) and Lucas Guariglia (LG)",
            "recipient": "Both parties (recorded conversation)",
            "title_subject": "LG admits Amazon and running event no JZ",
            "file_size_bytes": 80074
          },
          "summary": "Recorded phone conversation on November 15, 2022 between Joseph Zangrilli (JZ) and Lucas Guariglia (LG) at Rowboat Creative LLC. LG admits to using the Rowboat business Amazon account to purchase equipment for an event under Two Lane/Constellation without informing JZ, and confirms past undisclosed profit-sharing with a third party (Suzanne). LG states he wants to explore exiting the partnership due to feeling trapped and unable to continue the relationship. JZ repeatedly requests direct communication and agrees to pursue a business mediator or operating agreement.",
          "tags": [
            "FRAUD",
            "FIDUCIARY",
            "MISAPPROPRIATION",
            "CONTRACT",
            "TIMELINE",
            "ADMISSION"
          ],
